divs: Sighting Detailsi was driving on Congress ave.@ I-95 heading south approximately at 9:30 p.m. March 30th 2010 when i noticed a green fireball from the east heading west slowly descending but never saw a landing. it only lasted a few seconds after disappearing over the tree tops. i thought it was the coolest thing ever and have always wanted to see a meteor.
Summary: looked like a small green meteor
